    <h1>iPhone Tips & Tricks</h1>
    <p>Discover some hidden features and shortcuts to make the most of your iPhone.</p>

    <h2>Accessibility Shortcuts</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>**Invert Colors:** Quickly invert the colors on your screen for easier viewing in low-light conditions.</li>
        <li>**AssistiveTouch:** Create a customizable on-screen button for easy access to various functions.</li>
        <li>**VoiceOver:** Explore the powerful screen reader for accessibility features.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Productivity Boosters</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>**App Library:** Organize your apps into categories for easy navigation.</li>
        <li>**Back Tap:** Perform actions like taking screenshots or activating Siri with double or triple taps on the back of your device.</li>
        <li>**Focus:** Customize your device to minimize distractions and stay focused on the task at hand.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Camera and Photos</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>**Take Burst Photos:** Capture a series of photos quickly by holding down the shutter button.</li>
        <li>**Live Photos:** Capture moments with motion and sound.</li>
        <li>**Edit Photos:** Easily adjust brightness, contrast, and other settings within the Photos app.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>This is just a small selection of the many tips and tricks available for your iPhone. Explore the settings and features of your device to discover more!</p>
